                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def2-353-18740504 t18740504-353-punishment-21"></join>Two Years' Imprisonment.</rs>
                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">McVICAR</hi>—<hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18740504-353-punishment-22" type="punishmentDescription">
